00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:14.120
What's your next plan?

00:22:17.280 --> 00:22:17.840
Tu Da,

00:22:22.120 --> 00:22:23.120
move there.

00:22:25.480 --> 00:22:26.640
Everything's done.

00:22:27.440 --> 00:22:28.480
Those civilians,

00:22:28.600 --> 00:22:30.680
they're even more enthusiastic about catching assassins than we are.

00:22:30.680 --> 00:22:32.740
They catch nearly a hundred each day.

00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:35.280
The prison is almost full.

00:22:36.680 --> 00:22:37.680
That's good.

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:40.620
You don't have to hang around me all day anymore.

00:22:41.040 --> 00:22:43.200
You can go do things you want to do.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:46.000
Being stuck in one place is boring.

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:46.880
Mr. Xu,

00:22:47.280 --> 00:22:49.840
we enjoy following Miss Xiaofei.

00:22:50.040 --> 00:22:52.280
Besides, she has taught us a lot.

00:22:52.680 --> 00:22:53.940
You don't understand.

00:22:55.120 --> 00:22:56.780
I'm already being so tactful.

00:22:57.200 --> 00:22:58.840
You really think you're being productive?

00:22:58.840 --> 00:23:00.640
All day wasting time with trivial pursuits.

00:23:00.640 --> 00:23:02.440
Not behaving like Jinwu Guards at all.

00:23:02.440 --> 00:23:04.640
Go back and practice your martial arts.

00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:07.640
Come on,

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:09.570
everyone gather up!

00:23:13.760 --> 00:23:14.760
Really...

00:23:19.280 --> 00:23:20.120
Brothers,

00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:21.650
General Qin,

00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:23.180
before departing,

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:25.060
I have something important to do.

00:23:25.200 --> 00:23:27.660
The other enemies were not my personal foes.

00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:30.400
But the one who burned down my house

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:32.060
I must capture him myself.

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:32.770
Alright.

00:23:34.200 --> 00:23:36.120
Xiaofei, I'll be right back.

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:37.160
Be careful.

00:23:38.760 --> 00:23:40.600
Let's go.

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:42.400
Move.

00:23:56.640 --> 00:23:57.840
Isn't this a victory?

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:03.940
I really don't understand

00:24:04.200 --> 00:24:05.800
what your men were thinking.

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:07.680
Every sword used to assassinate me

00:24:07.680 --> 00:24:09.140
has 'Xing' engraved on it,

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:12.820
and they even kept receipts in duplicate from the blacksmith.

00:24:12.880 --> 00:24:14.360
So what if it was me?

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:16.280
I'll make you pay for this.

00:24:17.040 --> 00:24:18.170
All for Hua Xiaofei,

00:24:18.840 --> 00:24:19.960
that slut.

00:24:24.200 --> 00:24:26.520
You filthy scum.

00:24:27.640 --> 00:24:28.640
Take him to prison

00:24:29.240 --> 00:24:31.900
to await judgment from the Ministry of Justice.

00:24:33.960 --> 00:24:35.560
I don't have enough evidence

00:24:35.880 --> 00:24:37.880
to prove that you three were also involved.

00:24:37.880 --> 00:24:39.880
We certainly weren't, Magistrate Xu.

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:41.200
When we heard about your incident,

00:24:41.200 --> 00:24:42.530
our hearts were broken.

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:44.530
You are our local official,

00:24:44.680 --> 00:24:47.000
how could we possibly harm you?

00:24:47.600 --> 00:24:48.200
Exactly.

00:24:50.160 --> 00:24:51.440
You've brought so many people here.

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:52.600
Kill us if you want.

00:24:53.040 --> 00:24:53.840
It's up to you.

00:24:53.960 --> 00:24:55.160
I've already told you

00:24:55.200 --> 00:24:56.960
I have no evidence to arrest you.

00:24:56.960 --> 00:24:58.640
You can still remain in the chamber of commerce.

00:24:58.640 --> 00:24:59.480
I can prove it.

00:25:10.840 --> 00:25:13.440
The other three elders are also involved in this matter.

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:15.900
They can all be thrown into prison together.

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:19.360
Master Xu, it's been a while.

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:21.960
Fang Lihen.

00:25:23.200 --> 00:25:25.440
I've always treated you well.

00:25:26.680 --> 00:25:28.410
Why are you turning against me?

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:29.280
Ali.

00:25:29.760 --> 00:25:32.620
Are you going to expose the chamber's wrongdoings?

00:25:36.680 --> 00:25:37.540
I will testify.

00:25:38.200 --> 00:25:40.440
The assassination attempt against Master Xu

00:25:40.440 --> 00:25:42.440
was a conspiracy by the Four Elders.

00:25:42.840 --> 00:25:43.640
Arrest them!

