00:25:57.640 --> 00:25:59.840
and disrupt the guild's normal operations.

00:25:59.840 --> 00:26:01.170
Furthermore, Master Xu

00:26:01.200 --> 00:26:03.920
had multiple previous conflicts with the guild,

00:26:03.920 --> 00:26:06.120
planting the seeds of discord long ago.

00:26:06.640 --> 00:26:08.480
Therefore, the Chamber of Commerce has decided

00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:09.940
to assassinate Master Xu.

00:26:09.960 --> 00:26:11.120
I knew it.

00:26:11.200 --> 00:26:13.720
All these years, you've been nothing but an ungrateful wolf.

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:16.000
I never thought that you, this little lamb,

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:17.600
would be capable of such a thing.

00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:19.160
The descendant of a criminal official

00:26:19.160 --> 00:26:20.360
is nothing but trash.

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:23.480
This will destroy our Chamber of Commerce.

00:26:23.480 --> 00:26:25.360
What benefit does this bring you?

00:26:25.480 --> 00:26:26.520
What benefit?

00:26:27.640 --> 00:26:30.040
You simply want to take my place.

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:31.880
Am I right?

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:38.770
The witness is here.

00:26:38.960 --> 00:26:41.120
I hope you will uphold justice, Mr. Xu

00:26:41.400 --> 00:26:43.530
and throw all four elders into prison.

00:26:45.240 --> 00:26:48.360
I, Fang Lihen, will testify about the crimes of the four elders

00:26:48.360 --> 00:26:49.820
and tell everything I know

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.760
without holding anything back.

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:54.440
Mr. Xu.

00:26:55.640 --> 00:26:57.240
They were trying to kill you.

00:26:57.840 --> 00:26:59.040
How can you show mercy

00:26:59.120 --> 00:27:00.720
to those who wanted you dead?

00:27:12.680 --> 00:27:15.280
I cannot wrongfully accuse any innocent person

00:27:15.280 --> 00:27:16.810
nor can I kill the innocent.

00:27:17.240 --> 00:27:19.300
If every official in the Tang Dynasty

00:27:19.400 --> 00:27:21.440
ruled based on personal preferences

00:27:21.440 --> 00:27:23.440
and personal grudges,

00:27:24.040 --> 00:27:25.970
then the country would fall apart.

00:27:28.600 --> 00:27:30.880
Take Elder Xing to prison

00:27:31.240 --> 00:27:33.000
to await the Ministry of Justice's verdict.

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.660
As for the other three elders,

00:27:34.680 --> 00:27:36.200
take them to the magistrate's office first,

00:27:36.200 --> 00:27:37.660
and after interrogation,

00:27:37.880 --> 00:27:39.120
we will decide their fate.

00:27:39.120 --> 00:27:39.920
Yes.

00:27:40.200 --> 00:27:41.060
Take them away.

00:27:45.840 --> 00:27:46.640
Fang Lihen,

00:27:47.680 --> 00:27:48.480
remember.

00:27:57.480 --> 00:27:58.080
Li.

00:27:59.040 --> 00:28:01.640
Now that the four elders have lost their power,

00:28:01.880 --> 00:28:03.480
you might as well surrender.

00:28:03.480 --> 00:28:05.520
Tell us everything the guild has done

00:28:05.520 --> 00:28:06.520
over these years.

00:28:06.920 --> 00:28:07.600
This way,

00:28:07.760 --> 00:28:10.160
you might have a chance to redeem yourself.

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:13.120
I will petition the court to protect you

00:28:13.440 --> 00:28:15.520
and bring your parents back to Chang'an soon.

00:28:15.520 --> 00:28:17.640
When I heard you died from poisoning,

00:28:18.640 --> 00:28:19.440
I felt

00:28:20.000 --> 00:28:21.240
extremely sad.

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:23.160
In Chang'an,

00:28:23.520 --> 00:28:24.920
you were my only brother.

00:28:24.920 --> 00:28:25.920
I thought,

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:27.530
if you were really gone,

00:28:28.600 --> 00:28:29.640
I would truly be

00:28:30.520 --> 00:28:31.760
all alone.

00:28:33.800 --> 00:28:34.860
But unexpectedly,

00:28:35.240 --> 00:28:36.440
you faked your death.

00:28:37.400 --> 00:28:40.760
And I knew nothing about it from beginning to end.

00:28:41.640 --> 00:28:44.040
Because of my identity as an imperial detective,

00:28:44.040 --> 00:28:46.570
I couldn't tell anyone about faking my death.

00:28:48.760 --> 00:28:51.290
You investigated the guild as a secret agent.

00:28:51.600 --> 00:28:53.930
While investigating the guild by my side,

00:28:53.960 --> 00:28:55.690
did you truly see me as a brother

00:28:55.960 --> 00:28:57.360
or were you just using me?

00:28:58.160 --> 00:28:59.290
If you were using me,

00:28:59.600 --> 00:29:01.600
you certainly treated me very well.

00:29:02.520 --> 00:29:04.200
But if you considered me a brother,

00:29:04.200 --> 00:29:07.260
why did you never consider things from my perspective?

00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:09.400
Xu Ziqi,

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.880
I can no longer trust you.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:17.420
Now that all four elders have been captured,

00:29:17.920 --> 00:29:19.480
you've gotten what you wanted.

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:20.600
From now on,

00:29:21.600 --> 00:29:22.800
the guild's affairs,

00:29:23.480 --> 00:29:24.440
my affairs,

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:27.200
stay out of all of it.

00:29:29.400 --> 00:29:31.000
Ali! Ali!

00:29:53.520 --> 00:29:54.200
Sir,

00:29:56.840 --> 00:29:58.170
must you really do this?

00:29:59.160 --> 00:29:59.960
Right now,

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:03.000
I can only pledge my allegiance to Master Wu.

00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:04.260
Master Wu loves money.

00:30:04.360 --> 00:30:06.160
If I don't offer him some wealth,

00:30:06.720 --> 00:30:09.240
how will he know I'm obedient enough?

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:11.080
That I'm capable enough?

00:30:11.720 --> 00:30:14.050
How would he let me replace the four elders

00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:15.880
and truly control the guild?

00:30:16.640 --> 00:30:19.040
But, but this is too much, sir!

00:30:23.480 --> 00:30:24.120
Sir,

00:30:24.840 --> 00:30:26.440
how can you put all your chips

00:30:26.600 --> 00:30:28.440
on this Master Wu?

00:30:28.520 --> 00:30:30.680
You two have never even met!

00:30:31.160 --> 00:30:32.960
Master Wu's usual methods,

00:30:33.480 --> 00:30:34.880
as you've heard,

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:36.930
he's not exactly a good person.

00:30:37.200 --> 00:30:38.000
Yang Lin.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.040
Do you remember

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:43.060
what this mansion used to be like?

00:30:45.200 --> 00:30:46.130
In the mornings,

00:30:46.200 --> 00:30:46.720
Father

00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:50.080
would recite books with me in the corridor.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:54.200
Mother would bring us soup she made herself.

00:30:54.680 --> 00:30:57.360
At meals, the family would sit together

00:30:58.200 --> 00:31:00.000
and chat about everyday things.

00:31:01.200 --> 00:31:02.200
I don't want to...

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:04.200
I really don't want to be alone

00:31:04.200 --> 00:31:06.240
living in this empty house anymore.

00:31:08.720 --> 00:31:10.850
No matter how many possessions I have,

00:31:11.520 --> 00:31:12.680
they're still cold.

00:31:15.280 --> 00:31:18.140
What does it matter if Master Wu isn't a good person?

00:31:18.680 --> 00:31:20.680
As long as he's capable.

00:31:21.720 --> 00:31:22.440
But sir,

00:31:22.960 --> 00:31:25.240
this is Miss Xiaofei's golden statue!

00:31:27.760 --> 00:31:29.020
When the heart is gone,

00:31:29.200 --> 00:31:31.330
keeping these things is meaningless.

00:31:31.840 --> 00:31:32.640
Consider it

00:31:33.600 --> 00:31:35.120
my farewell to Xiaofei.

00:31:37.280 --> 00:31:39.640
Take it out and melt it down.

00:31:59.040 --> 00:31:59.840
Xu Ziqi.

00:32:00.160 --> 00:32:00.960
Look.

00:32:01.760 --> 00:32:02.680
That's a tree.

00:32:03.360 --> 00:32:04.290
That's a flower.

00:32:04.720 --> 00:32:05.920
Look at those clouds.

00:32:06.720 --> 00:32:07.680
And that bird.

00:32:09.640 --> 00:32:10.240
Xiaofei.

00:32:11.240 --> 00:32:13.440
Even though I used to see them every day,

00:32:13.440 --> 00:32:15.560
now that I've been given a second chance,

00:32:15.560 --> 00:32:17.220
everything looks different.

00:32:18.680 --> 00:32:19.940
The trees are so green.

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:23.010
The clouds are so white.

00:32:24.160 --> 00:32:25.690
The flowers are so vibrant.

00:32:26.200 --> 00:32:27.930
And the birds are so beautiful.

00:32:28.200 --> 00:32:28.840
Xiaofei,

00:32:30.600 --> 00:32:31.860
you're beautiful too.

00:32:35.280 --> 00:32:36.280
When I think about

00:32:36.880 --> 00:32:37.920
our nice house

00:32:37.920 --> 00:32:40.440
burning down after less than 20 days,

00:32:40.600 --> 00:32:41.730
it makes me so angry.

00:32:42.160 --> 00:32:43.040
It's okay.

00:32:43.200 --> 00:32:45.440
Manager Xing paid us good compensation.

00:32:45.440 --> 00:32:47.280
As long as we still have the land,

00:32:47.520 --> 00:32:48.960
rebuilding will be fine.

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:50.400
We can even improve the layout.

00:32:50.400 --> 00:32:50.800
Right.

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.290
The previous layout

00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:54.200
had a living room that was too big and bedrooms too small.

00:32:54.200 --> 00:32:55.600
The kitchen was too small too.

00:32:55.600 --> 00:32:56.660
It affects your...

00:33:01.040 --> 00:33:02.120
Wait,

00:33:02.600 --> 00:33:04.330
isn't this our previous house?

00:33:04.680 --> 00:33:06.800
How is it still here after the fire?

00:33:11.720 --> 00:33:12.250
Let's go.

00:33:22.280 --> 00:33:23.680
Mr. Xu.

00:33:23.840 --> 00:33:24.600
Mr. Xu.

00:33:25.120 --> 00:33:25.720
Mr. Xu.

00:33:25.840 --> 00:33:26.600
Mr. Xu.

00:33:26.600 --> 00:33:28.440
Mr. Xu loves his country and its people.

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:30.600
How could we let such a good official

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:32.800
not even have a place to live?

00:33:32.960 --> 00:33:33.200
Today.

00:33:33.200 --> 00:33:33.680
Indeed.

00:33:33.680 --> 00:33:36.600
We found the original blueprints of the house.

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:37.840
Working day and night,

00:33:37.840 --> 00:33:38.970
everyone pitched in

00:33:39.600 --> 00:33:41.360
to rebuild this house for you.

00:33:41.760 --> 00:33:44.000
It's identical inside and out,

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:46.200
down to the smallest detail.

00:33:46.440 --> 00:33:48.760
Yes. Madam, would you like

00:33:49.240 --> 00:33:50.440
to take a look inside?

00:33:55.760 --> 00:33:56.720
Let's go.

00:34:05.280 --> 00:34:06.120
Not too bad.

00:34:08.239 --> 00:34:09.500
It's exactly the same.

00:34:13.560 --> 00:34:15.360
Thank you all for your help, neighbors.

00:34:15.360 --> 00:34:16.719
After we get settled,

00:34:16.920 --> 00:34:19.600
I'll personally visit each of you to express my gratitude.

00:34:19.600 --> 00:34:21.960
Then we'll be expecting Mr. Xu and Mrs. Xu

00:34:22.239 --> 00:34:23.880
to come over for a drink.

00:34:25.400 --> 00:34:27.239
We won't disturb you two any longer.

00:34:27.239 --> 00:34:28.100
We're leaving.

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:29.489
Let's go.

