What did you have in mind then?

00:34:57.240 --> 00:34:58.300
What are you doing?

00:35:04.320 --> 00:35:05.080
Xiaofei,

00:35:05.480 --> 00:35:06.320
what's wrong?

00:35:06.880 --> 00:35:09.440
I'm thinking about what to do next.

00:35:11.640 --> 00:35:13.570
Now that things have settled down,

00:35:13.600 --> 00:35:15.960
I plan to focus on my career again.

00:35:17.000 --> 00:35:18.400
I want to get rich.

00:35:18.480 --> 00:35:19.760
It might be difficult

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:21.500
with just my little treasure.

00:35:22.440 --> 00:35:23.500
But I can't give up.

00:35:23.840 --> 00:35:24.560
So,

00:35:24.920 --> 00:35:25.960
I'll try my best

00:35:26.360 --> 00:35:27.820
to remain a female tycoon.

00:35:29.400 --> 00:35:31.880
What about you? What are your plans?

00:35:32.600 --> 00:35:34.930
First, we need to set up our home properly.

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:37.920
I'm thinking of getting a bigger bed.

00:35:38.080 --> 00:35:40.920
That way when we sleep together,

00:35:41.720 --> 00:35:43.120
we won't easily roll off.

00:35:43.720 --> 00:35:44.240
Then,

00:35:44.720 --> 00:35:46.320
we need a large dining table,

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:48.290
an extremely large one.

00:35:48.840 --> 00:35:50.100
And most importantly,

00:35:50.480 --> 00:35:52.240
although my identity as an imperial detective

00:35:52.240 --> 00:35:53.360
has been exposed,

00:35:54.120 --> 00:35:57.080
I still need to continue investigating the chamber of commerce matter.

00:35:57.080 --> 00:35:59.340
While the four elders are under control,

00:35:59.440 --> 00:36:01.480
I plan to interrogate them thoroughly

00:36:01.480 --> 00:36:04.000
to find out where the account book is hidden.

00:36:06.840 --> 00:36:09.280
It's just one account book,

00:36:10.360 --> 00:36:13.000
how can it be so impossible to find?

00:36:14.960 --> 00:36:18.400
Maybe it's not an ordinary account book.

00:36:18.960 --> 00:36:19.960
That makes sense.

00:36:20.760 --> 00:36:21.490
For example?

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:22.840
Well,

00:36:22.920 --> 00:36:24.160
it could be

00:36:24.160 --> 00:36:25.800
an emotionless learning machine,

00:36:25.800 --> 00:36:27.260
memorizing the accounts.

00:36:27.360 --> 00:36:29.090
Actually just a living person.

00:36:29.480 --> 00:36:31.520
That seems quite far-fetched.

00:36:33.080 --> 00:36:34.080
Or

00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:38.480
maybe it's hidden in a secret cellar

00:36:39.040 --> 00:36:40.320
guarded by monsters,

00:36:40.880 --> 00:36:42.440
perhaps a three-headed dog

00:36:43.240 --> 00:36:44.840
or a giant spider.

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:48.040
Or maybe there's a snake

00:36:48.160 --> 00:36:50.220
that turns you to stone with one look.

00:36:54.400 --> 00:36:55.040
Xiaofei,

00:36:55.640 --> 00:36:57.640
you should focus on making money.

00:36:57.880 --> 00:37:00.280
Leave the investigation to me.

00:37:02.160 --> 00:37:02.960
Alright!

00:37:19.400 --> 00:37:21.000
Sir, the person has arrived.

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:29.420
Why don't you remove the blindfold covering your eyes?

00:37:31.720 --> 00:37:33.320
What you wish for me to see,

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:34.520
I will surely see.

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:36.760
What you don't wish for me to see,

00:37:37.280 --> 00:37:39.160
I wouldn't dare look at all.

00:37:41.640 --> 00:37:42.440
Take it off.

00:37:52.960 --> 00:37:54.440
The items you presented,

00:37:55.320 --> 00:37:56.180
I've seen them,

00:37:56.440 --> 00:37:57.480
I like them very much,

00:37:57.480 --> 00:37:58.480
and I accept them.

00:37:58.960 --> 00:37:59.800
If you

00:38:00.480 --> 00:38:01.880
have any requests of me,

00:38:02.040 --> 00:38:03.280
feel free to speak.

00:38:08.360 --> 00:38:11.280
I beg you to grant me real authority in the guild,

00:38:11.520 --> 00:38:13.120
to give me a chance

00:38:13.400 --> 00:38:15.000
to make something of myself.

00:38:16.360 --> 00:38:18.880
Living without seeking comfort and peace,

00:38:19.160 --> 00:38:21.620
insisting on making achievements instead.

00:38:21.880 --> 00:38:22.960
You young people,

00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:26.400
do you truly understand what it means that 'the wise adapt to circumstances'?

00:38:26.400 --> 00:38:27.760
Being born in prosperous times -

00:38:27.760 --> 00:38:29.120
these are the circumstances.

00:38:29.120 --> 00:38:30.360
Not fighting, not grabbing,

00:38:30.360 --> 00:38:30.960
not competing,

00:38:30.960 --> 00:38:33.160
knowing your place - that's being wise.

00:38:33.440 --> 00:38:35.040
What achievements do you seek?

00:38:35.040 --> 00:38:36.800
To cause trouble for the court?

00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:40.640
If you want achievements,

00:38:40.920 --> 00:38:43.640
comfort and peace are certainly not what you seek.

00:38:43.640 --> 00:38:46.480
Speak. What do you really want?

00:38:50.160 --> 00:38:52.890
I am the son of the disgraced official Fang Siyou.

00:38:53.160 --> 00:38:54.360
I want to find a patron

00:38:54.840 --> 00:38:57.440
to clear me of the stigma of being a criminal's son.

00:38:57.440 --> 00:38:58.960
You young people

00:38:59.160 --> 00:39:00.960
still don't see through the ways of this world.

00:39:00.960 --> 00:39:03.920
A stain is something that can never be truly cleaned.

00:39:04.320 --> 00:39:05.520
When the stain is gone,

00:39:05.520 --> 00:39:06.980
the fabric is also ruined.

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:08.760
It ruins both the appearance

00:39:08.760 --> 00:39:09.920
and the substance.

00:39:13.720 --> 00:39:16.080
Sir, I have nowhere else to turn.

00:39:16.880 --> 00:39:17.440
Sir.

00:39:17.640 --> 00:39:19.640
You are this humble one's last hope.

00:39:29.240 --> 00:39:30.000
You're

00:39:30.240 --> 00:39:31.560
quite obedient indeed.

00:39:31.560 --> 00:39:33.360
You've given me such a nice gift,

00:39:33.600 --> 00:39:35.060
I should return the favor.

00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:37.000
Come on, bring it in.

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:44.960
Boss.

00:39:45.400 --> 00:39:47.880
Didn't we agree to conduct an interrogation?

00:39:47.880 --> 00:39:48.880
What's all this?

00:39:49.280 --> 00:39:50.610
It looks like an ambush.

00:39:51.640 --> 00:39:53.240
We're doing serious work here.

00:39:53.240 --> 00:39:55.400
We finally caught these four elders.

00:39:55.640 --> 00:39:56.640
Of course we need to interrogate them

00:39:56.640 --> 00:39:58.560
thoroughly and completely.

00:39:59.360 --> 00:40:00.120
So...

00:40:01.840 --> 00:40:03.840
We brought our own supplies.

00:40:04.080 --> 00:40:05.440
Boss, boss.

00:40:07.800 --> 00:40:09.730
Something terrible has happened!

00:40:09.880 --> 00:40:10.640
Open it!

00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:26.360
Sir,

00:40:26.600 --> 00:40:27.600
I've been disrespectful.

00:40:27.600 --> 00:40:28.560
Please punish me,

00:40:28.560 --> 00:40:29.320
sir.

00:40:30.000 --> 00:40:31.400
These elders of the guild

00:40:31.920 --> 00:40:33.240
have little loyalty,

00:40:33.640 --> 00:40:34.960
yet plenty of schemes.

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:36.760
They're so disobedient

00:40:37.240 --> 00:40:38.970
and reckless in their actions.

00:40:39.280 --> 00:40:41.810
Keeping them around will only cause trouble.

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:47.140
Take them away.

00:40:57.120 --> 00:40:59.480
I've had someone remove those items.

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:01.840
You can open your eyes now.

00:41:12.440 --> 00:41:15.760
Sir, may I ask where Elder Yi is now?

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:19.640
Elder Yi has confessed to the corruption charges

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:22.050
and will be executed tomorrow at noon.

00:41:22.920 --> 00:41:24.520
Elder Yi has been good to you,

00:41:24.760 --> 00:41:25.880
I am aware of that.

00:41:26.360 --> 00:41:27.760
Go see her one last time.

00:41:28.360 --> 00:41:30.360
Reminisce and share your thoughts,

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:32.120
and also resolve some

00:41:32.400 --> 00:41:33.800
unfinished matters.

00:41:35.360 --> 00:41:36.690
Unfinished matters...

00:41:37.360 --> 00:41:38.760
It's getting late today.

00:41:39.400 --> 00:41:40.800
You should head home now.

00:41:42.720 --> 00:41:43.780
I understand, sir.

00:41:44.120 --> 00:41:45.450
I will take my leave now.

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:47.320
I'll go now.

00:41:51.240 --> 00:41:52.000
You may go.

00:41:54.920 --> 00:41:56.160
Sir, do you think

00:41:56.440 --> 00:41:58.520
that Fang Lihen is someone we can use?

00:41:58.840 --> 00:42:01.240
He seems naive and easy to control.

00:42:01.840 --> 00:42:02.880
But people,

00:42:03.240 --> 00:42:05.170
who doesn't have their own agenda?

00:42:06.280 --> 00:42:07.720
Go and watch carefully

00:42:07.960 --> 00:42:09.000
what he said

00:42:09.120 --> 00:42:10.640
to Yi Rusu in the prison.

00:42:12.080 --> 00:42:13.040
This Yi Rusu,

00:42:13.480 --> 00:42:15.520
is she hiding something from me?

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:19.000
Yes.

00:42:43.040 --> 00:42:44.640
Go see her one last time.

00:42:44.960 --> 00:42:46.120
She's dying.

00:42:46.480 --> 00:42:49.440
Do you still want to keep secrets in this world?

00:42:57.520 --> 00:42:58.360
Elder Yi.

00:42:59.240 --> 00:43:01.800
These are all prepared for you by Xiaofei.

00:43:02.560 --> 00:43:03.920
She said in this prison,

00:43:04.080 --> 00:43:06.600
toiletries are in short supply.

00:43:07.080 --> 00:43:08.000
Since you're

00:43:08.160 --> 00:43:09.420
always so meticulous,

00:43:09.920 --> 00:43:11.850
she prepared these things for you.

00:43:11.960 --> 00:43:14.320
They're not expensive items though.

00:43:14.560 --> 00:43:15.690
Please bear with it.

00:43:16.440 --> 00:43:17.280
Last night,

00:43:17.800 --> 00:43:19.660
the three of them never returned.

00:43:20.240 --> 00:43:21.160
I knew

00:43:21.760 --> 00:43:23.160
they wouldn't come back.

00:43:24.600 --> 00:43:25.440
Elder Yi.

00:43:26.040 --> 00:43:27.700
There's something important

00:43:27.960 --> 00:43:29.160
I must ask you.

00:43:29.880 --> 00:43:31.920
Is there a book in the guild that...

00:43:37.240 --> 00:43:38.170
Why are you here?

00:43:39.120 --> 00:43:40.650
I've come to visit Elder Yi.

00:43:41.360 --> 00:43:42.420
Is that necessary?

00:43:59.120 --> 00:44:01.600
Master Xu, could you give us some privacy?

00:44:02.480 --> 00:44:03.440
I have something

00:44:04.640 --> 00:44:05.960
to say to Fang Lihen.

00:44:24.360 --> 00:44:25.000
Elder Yi.

00:44:25.480 --> 00:44:27.280
I know you want to replace me

00:44:27.440 --> 00:44:29.040
and that's why you framed me.

00:44:29.360 --> 00:44:31.890
But I never thought Mr. Wu would be so ruthless

00:44:32.360 --> 00:44:34.560
that he would take all four of our lives.

00:44:36.320 --> 00:44:38.560
Is there any way to get you out of here?

00:44:38.960 --> 00:44:41.080
It's too late. I have no choice.

00:44:42.960 --> 00:44:44.290
I'm going to die anyway.

00:44:45.360 --> 00:44:46.120
Elder Yi.

00:44:46.440 --> 00:44:46.880
I...

00:44:46.880 --> 00:44:48.760
You don't need to apologize to me.

00:44:49.160 --> 00:44:49.880
Fang Lihen.

00:44:50.120 --> 00:44:52.980
You've been oppressed by the guild for so many years

00:44:53.360 --> 00:44:54.760
and suffered so much.

00:44:55.320 --> 00:44:57.450
The guild is indeed falling apart now.

00:44:57.640 --> 00:45:00.040
You made a choice to protect yourself.

00:45:00.760 --> 00:45:02.600
There's nothing wrong with that.

00:45:02.600 --> 00:45:03.480
Besides,

00:45:03.880 --> 00:45:06.800
what the four of us did was truly heinous.

00:45:08.240 --> 00:45:09.640
Since joining the guild,

00:45:11.960 --> 00:45:14.120
I've always known I might die a gruesome death.

00:45:14.120 --> 00:45:15.780
I've thought about it before.

00:45:18.480 --> 00:45:19.610
What's with all this

00:45:19.760 --> 00:45:20.440
commotion?

00:45:20.640 --> 00:45:21.520
Noon approaches.

00:45:21.520 --> 00:45:24.120
The prisoner Yi Rusu will be escorted to the execution ground.

00:45:24.120 --> 00:45:24.960
Today...

00:45:25.400 --> 00:45:26.400
Mr. Wu.

00:45:26.640 --> 00:45:29.240
He must have someone watching your every move,

00:45:29.480 --> 00:45:30.320
to see if

00:45:30.320 --> 00:45:32.760
you can still help him gather some information.

00:45:32.760 --> 00:45:35.160
Shouldn't they at least give the person time to clean up?

00:45:35.160 --> 00:45:38.220
It'll only take about half an incense stick. Just wait.

00:45:42.960 --> 00:45:44.640
The chamber of commerce has a ledger.

00:45:44.640 --> 00:45:46.840
I've hidden it inside the courtesan's portrait.

00:45:46.840 --> 00:45:48.440
Find the courtesan's portrait.

00:45:48.440 --> 00:45:50.760
This item must never be given to Master Wu.

00:45:50.760 --> 00:45:52.360
This man is heartless

00:45:52.360 --> 00:45:53.520
and completely untrustworthy.

00:45:53.520 --> 00:45:56.440
You must find the ledger and keep it to protect yourself.

00:45:56.440 --> 00:45:57.200
Do you understand?